@VoyageVoyage.Server_HostAddress = http://localhost:5066

### Get current authenticated user (stateful -- reflects request-scoped identity)
GET {{VoyageVoyage.Server_HostAddress}}/api/users/me

###

### List all trips
GET {{VoyageVoyage.Server_HostAddress}}/api/trips

###

### Get a trip by id
GET {{VoyageVoyage.Server_HostAddress}}/api/trips/1

###

### Create a new trip
POST {{VoyageVoyage.Server_HostAddress}}/api/trips
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2026-06-01",
  "endDate": "2026-06-03",
  "destination": "Paris",
  "status": "planned"
}

###

### Update an existing trip
PUT {{VoyageVoyage.Server_HostAddress}}/api/trips/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2026-04-06",
  "endDate": "2026-04-08",
  "destination": "Lyon",
  "status": "confirmed"
}

###

### Delete a trip
DELETE {{VoyageVoyage.Server_HostAddress}}/api/trips/1

###
